      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really nice shape and has clearly been well-loved\u2014runs like a charm and is ready for its next adventure! If you're looking for a dependable car that still looks great on the road, this is the one for you. I've taken great care of it, and I'm sure you'll love it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you want to come see it!",
