    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This A80-generation icon features the legendary 2JZ-GTE twin-turbocharged inline-six, delivering power through the robust Getrag V160 6-speed manual gearbox. The sequential CT12B turbochargers spool predictably, providing a linear torque curve, while the factory Torsen limited-slip differential ensures optimal power delivery out of corners. The chassis remains composed on its double-wishbone suspension, benefiting from recent bushing replacements and a fresh alignment. Mechanically sorted with a documented timing belt service and a clean cooling system, this Supra is an exceptional performer for the purist who values drivetrain precision and forced-induction heritage.",
      "price": 38500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
