    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Up for sale is a truly well-preserved example that strikes the perfect balance between a daily driver and an enthusiast's pride. The exterior paint retains a deep, lustrous finish, showing only the minor, inevitable stone chips from light highway use. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary; the premium leather seats are supple with no cracks or bolster wear, and the carpets have been protected by floor mats since day one. Mechanically, this car is in excellent health. The engine idles smoothly and delivers power across the rev range without hesitation, while the gearbox provides crisp, confident shifts. It has been fastidiously maintained with a complete service history, including recent fluid flushes and a fresh set of high-performance tires. Every feature, from the ice-cold climate control to the intuitive infotainment system, works flawlessly. This is a solid, honest vehicle that is ready to be driven and enjoyed immediately.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
